@MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5256

### Start a new conversation
POST {{MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Hello! My name is Alice."
}

### Continue the conversation (replace with actual conversationId from previous response)
POST {{MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "conversationId": "YOUR-CONVERSATION-ID-HERE",
    "message": "What is my name?"
}

### Reset a conversation (replace with actual conversationId)
POST {{MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress}}/reset/YOUR-CONVERSATION-ID-HERE

### Health check
GET {{MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### Liveness check
GET {{MafStatefulApi.Api_HostAddress}}/alive
